{"tid":2106542,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人唔食人口水尾","createTime":"2020-07-13T11:43:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-14T05:39:02.000Z","uid":249869,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a48b350764dafa41016493d3cc29fb0835cec56f","tid":2106542,"uid":249869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T11:43:38.000Z","msg":"好細個開始已經唔食人口水尾<br />\n甚至自己親生老母咬完一啖個包都唔想同一個位咬返落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲記得小學嗰時見到同學買一包紙包飲品<br />\n用同一枝管幾個人輪流啜仲問我飲唔飲真係 大開眼界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n後尾大咗知道原來好普遍好多人唔介意 <br />\n原來自己先係異類<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c04e2064d05cd377d49f4cf69ed092f50ded817c","tid":2106542,"uid":89368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T11:45:22.000Z","msg":"細個我都係咁，除左口水尾外阿媽阿爸啖我塊面我會抹，大左唔知咩時侯變到冇所謂"},{"pid":"79605f23702eb555895d1a345d62610cb2220a42","tid":2106542,"uid":249869,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c04e2064d05cd377d49f4cf69ed092f50ded817c","tid":2106542,"uid":89368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T11:45:22.000Z","msg":"細個我都係咁，除左口水尾外阿媽阿爸啖我塊面我會抹，大左唔知咩時侯變到冇所謂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T12:46:26.000Z","msg":"大咗都仲係有所謂<br />\n但好多時候唔好意思出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能個人廢"},{"pid":"7d60a2e9338da8ab7e4f3b2054a47f3f0ed1cef5","tid":2106542,"uid":159236,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T22:49:03.000Z","msg":"我<br />\n會想嘔"},{"pid":"410561617fe750b3f9d7337d89e37ac411d50616","tid":2106542,"uid":337525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T23:05:04.000Z","msg":"通常都係人地食我口水尾 <br />\nI mean 囡囡<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xXFEQRi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://